'''Viola Beach'''是一支[[英國|英國]]獨立流行音樂樂隊，在2013年組成，最後成員為克里斯‧伦纳德（Kris Leonard，結他手及主唱）、里弗‧里夫斯（River Reeves，結他手）、湯馬士·洛（Tomas Lowe，男低音）和杰克‧戴金（Jack Dakin，鼓手）。四名成員以及其經理人於2016年2月13日在[[瑞典|瑞典]]的一場交通意外中全部身亡<ref name="Guardian" /><ref name="bbcnews" /><ref name="nme" /><ref name="9net" /><ref name="mirror">{{cite news|last1=Keegan|first1=Simon|title=Who are Viola Beach? British band tragically killed after car plunges into canal in Sweden|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/who-viola-beach-british-band-7367681|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=Daily Mirror|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130054631/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/who-viola-beach-british-band-7367681}}</ref>。

== 生涯 ==
Viola Beach在2013年中成立，創始成員為克里斯‧伦纳德（結他手及主唱）、弗朗基‧库尔森（Frankie Coulson，結他手）、喬尼‧吉布森（Jonny Gibson，男低音）和杰克‧戴金（鼓手）<ref>{{cite web|title=Viola Beach|url=http://www.themusicmanual.co.uk/2014/01/viola-beach.html|website=The Music Manual|accessdate=14 February 2016|date=4 January 2014|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507072536/http://www.themusicmanual.co.uk/2014/01/viola-beach.html}}</ref>。在2015年5月，樂隊進行最後一次重組，原成員克里斯‧伦纳德和杰克‧戴金加上新成員里弗‧里夫斯（結他手）、湯馬士·洛（男低音）而成<ref name="lecho-guy">{{cite news|last1=Guy|first1=Peter|title=Viola Beach - Buzz Band of the Week|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/viola-beach-buzz-band-week-10412911|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=Liverpool Echo|date=12 November 2015|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825004546/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/viola-beach-buzz-band-week-10412911}}</ref><ref name="mmagazine">{{cite news|title=30 seconds interview: Viola Beach|url=http://www.m-magazine.co.uk/newmusic/30seconds/30-seconds-interview-viola-beach/|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=M|date=23 December 2015|archive-date=2018-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815080555/https://www.m-magazine.co.uk/newmusic/30seconds/30-seconds-interview-viola-beach/}}</ref>，在[[利物浦|利物浦]][[洞穴俱樂部|洞穴俱樂部]]首次亮相<ref name="express-mansfield">{{cite news|last1=Mansfield|first1=Katie|title=Who are Viola Beach? The tragic indie stars who got their big break while cleaning toilets|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/643960/Viola-Beach-car-crash-Sweden-Kris-Leonard-River-Reeves-Tomas-Lowe-Jack-Dakin-Craig-Tarry|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=Daily Express|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2019-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191126115110/https://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/643960/Viola-Beach-car-crash-Sweden-Kris-Leonard-River-Reeves-Tomas-Lowe-Jack-Dakin-Craig-Tarry}}</ref>。他們首支單曲"Swings and Waterslides" 在2015年9月被[[BBC廣播一台|BBC廣播一台]]加入播放列表<ref name="bbc-cobain">{{cite news|last1=Cobain|first1=Elise|title=On the playlist: Viola Beach - Swings & Waterslides|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/introducing/entries/e4dbcb6c-7537-4de4-9dc2-d8b99b6bf36e|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=BBC Introducing|date=3 September 2015|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129045657/https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/introducing/entries/e4dbcb6c-7537-4de4-9dc2-d8b99b6bf36e}}</ref>。

樂隊受到BBC Introducing的提拔，曾在[[里丁與里茲音樂節|里丁與里茲音樂節]]的BBC Introducing舞台上演出<ref name="lecho-guy"/><ref>{{cite news |first=Jess |last=Staufenberg |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/viola-beach-british-band-in-sweden-canal-crash-performed-at-leeds-and-reading-festivals-a6873111.html |title=Viola Beach: British band in Sweden canal crash performed at Leeds and Reading festivals |publisher=Independent News and Media |newspaper=The Independent |date=14 February 2016 |accessdate=14 February 2016 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825041313/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/viola-beach-british-band-in-sweden-canal-crash-performed-at-leeds-and-reading-festivals-a6873111.html }}</ref>。他們第二首單曲是"Boys That Sing"/"Like a Fool"，於2016年2月22日亮相<ref name="echo-tributes">{{cite news|first=Max|last=Margan|title=Family tributes to Viola Beach band members killed in car crash|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/news/liverpool-news/family-tributes-viola-beach-band-10891023|accessdate=15 February 2016|work=Liverpool Echo|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825003044/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/news/liverpool-news/family-tributes-viola-beach-band-10891023}}</ref>。

== 交通意外 ==
[[File:Södertälje_kanal,_flygfoto_2014-09-20.jpg|thumbnail]]

2016年2月13日，四名樂隊成員連同經理人在瑞典的E4高速公路的[[南泰利耶|南泰利耶]]運河[[開啟橋|直升橋]]路段遇上車禍，五人全數罹難<ref name="bbcnews">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-35572838|title=UK band Viola Beach 'killed in Swedish car crash'|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=14 February 2016|accessdate=14 February 2016|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216232436/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-35572838|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nme">{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/various-artists/91488|title=Members of UK band Viola Beach reportedly killed in Sweden car crash|work=NME.com|date=14 February 2016|accessdate=14 February 2016|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319192455/http://www.nme.com/news/various-artists/91488}}</ref><ref name="9net">{{cite web|url=http://www.9news.com.au/entertainment/2016/02/14/21/24/members-of-british-indie-band-viola-beach-among-five-killed-after-car-plunges-off-bridge-in-sweden|title=Members of British indie band Viola Beach among five killed after car plunges off bridge in Sweden|work=Nine Network|date=14 February 2016|accessdate=14 February 2016|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825004426/https://www.9news.com.au/entertainment/2016/02/14/21/24/members-of-british-indie-band-viola-beach-among-five-killed-after-car-plunges-off-bridge-in-sweden}}</ref>。目擊者表示當時橋正上升讓船通過，然而事故車輪卻直衝飛墜河裡<ref name="bbc-tribute">{{cite news|title=Viola Beach families pay tribute to band and manager|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-35574051|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202042654/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-35574051}}</ref>。樂隊在事發前一天參加了[[北雪平|北雪平]]的Where's the Music?音樂節<ref name="Guardian">{{cite news|last1=Khomami|first1=Nadia|last2=Meikle|first2=James|title=Members and manager of indie band Viola Beach die in car crash in Sweden|url=http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/feb/14/five-british-men-die-in-car-crash-in-stockholm-sweden|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2021-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211023145738/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/feb/14/five-british-men-die-in-car-crash-in-stockholm-sweden}}</ref>，原定下個演出為3月在[[美國|美國]][[奧斯汀|奧斯汀]]的[[西南偏南|西南偏南音樂節]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Viola Beach: Remembering the Warrington band|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/35573062/viola-beach-remembering-the-warrington-band|accessdate=14 February 2016|work=BBC Newsbeat|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2019-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003013821/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/35573062/viola-beach-remembering-the-warrington-band}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/viola-beach-sweden-car-crash_us_56c07b2fe4b08ffac1259d6c |title=British Rock Band Viola Beach Reported Killed In Car Crash In Sweden |publisher=Huffington Post |date=14 February 2016 |accessdate=14 February 2016 |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017072355/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/viola-beach-sweden-car-crash_us_56c07b2fe4b08ffac1259d6c }}</ref>。

在英國出現了一些紀念活動，2月14日[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英格蘭足球超級聯賽]][[曼城|曼城]]對[[熱刺|熱刺]]的賽事，球迷鼓掌以對曼城球迷的經理人克雷格‧塔里（Craig Tarry）的致意<ref name="indy-applause">{{cite news|last1=Critchley|first1=Mark|title=Viola Beach: Manchester City fans 'clap for Craig' and pay tribute to crash victim against Tottenham|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/viola-beach-victims-ex-girlfriend-asks-fans-to-clap-for-craig-in-fifth-minute-of-manchester-city-vs-a6873286.html|accessdate=15 February 2016|work=The Independent|date=14 February 2016|archive-date=2018-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208173645/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/viola-beach-victims-ex-girlfriend-asks-fans-to-clap-for-craig-in-fifth-minute-of-manchester-city-vs-a6873286.html}}</ref> 。樂隊粉絲發起社交媒體戰役，試圖把"Swings & Waterslides"推上[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]首位<ref name="mirror-charts">{{cite news|last1=Hooper|first1=Paul|last2=Merriman|first2=Rebecca|title=Viola Beach storm up the charts as fans campaign to get them to number one following tragic deaths|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/viola-beach-storm-up-charts-7372928|accessdate=15 February 2016|work=Daily Mirror|date=15 February 2016|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825073757/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/viola-beach-storm-up-charts-7372928}}</ref>。

樂隊成員遇難消息發佈後，唱片公司宣佈先前所有單曲收入會捐贈給成員及經理人的家屬<ref name="echo-tributes"/>。

